         //*          machine-readable format.                             *             
         //*                                                               *             
         //* Libraries:                                                    *             
         //*   - STEPLIB: Specifies the libraries where the compiler and   *             
         //*     its runtime libraries are located.                        *             
         //*   - SYSIN: Contains the COBOL source code to be compiled.     *             
